MGI2Ensembl.Rd

MGI-to-Ensembl gene identifier mappings

MGI2Ensembl()

Value

MGI2Ensembl.

Note

Updated 2020-10-05.

Examples

object <- MGI2Ensembl()

#> → Importing MGI-to-Ensembl gene ID mappings.
#> → Caching URL at <http://www.informatics.jax.org/downloads/reports/MGI_Gene_Model_Coord.rpt>.
#> → Importing 1638e27783543_MGI_Gene_Model_Coord.rpt at /Users/mike/Library/Caches/AcidGenomes using vroom::`vroom()`.
print(object)
